{"tid":85102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私家車炒上天悅邨行人路 兩人重傷倒地","createTime":"2017-01-18T05:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T05:48:39.000Z","uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"500a63f268469ccbfb0e6fee0cb5abba5c730edf","tid":85102,"uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"天水圍天悅邨悅泰樓，今早9時18分，一輛豐田私家車疑失控衝上行人路，撞毀工地帳篷，衝向大廈地下單車位，將一名落樓買餸的女途人撞至重傷。私家車撞向大廈外牆停下，車上司機亦告受傷，事後獲救出躺在女傷者旁，救援人員到場將兩人送院治理，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，肇事私家車原本停在50米外路邊，車上有兩夫婦，原本私家車由女方駕駛，但女司機停車離開現場後，男方坐上司機位踩油開車，先撞到前面一輛車輛車尾後，再失控剷上壆位撞倒一條燈柱，然後倒車再撞倒一條路牌，之後衝前直剷入行人路。據悉，男司機不良於行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170118&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56187479 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170118%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56187479%20&d=6owW%2FFrr8QAxZoJXmOkNa3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=25d2e36e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170118%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56187479%20&h=11ee2e4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170118&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56187479 </a>"},{"pid":"21f9aa6117ae4e5f922c57fd416f3ca768191ecd","tid":85102,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"咁似自殺嘅喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b15dbb2fbc3a2f68418a2cf59b48cc418d7387d","tid":85102,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"腳殘就唔撚好揸車啦 正撚樣"},{"pid":"bf319b7411b9aac9cfb4419490f19303191bc6a8","tid":85102,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323a78b3df6689d9232bbff71cc65b63e325e0bc","tid":85102,"uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<im