eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2F133625_da692fd0ea8960e28833f2bd48a54d81.jpg&h=958c29b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5953a6d9ac567a40c7fbec952b48940cb4533a63","tid":85102,"uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmToVLbVeFZfnKNAdhGPa5BhWBjk5gMBtkk8dUh2GsDQEv?filename=2Y8WJ26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Y8WJ26.jpg&h=1844a4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車撞向大廈外牆停下(讀者林先生攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmen4s48zywuEmM9MzY6FmyZ6Hr9JmM49EtMxaD6BaeYwx?filename=mq4ONYm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmq4ONYm.jpg&h=4e087bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車撞女途人（右）。遠處躺地男子為私家車司機(fb&lrm;小心駕駛討論區圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ917nvCSLZi5RiVx4Kw84MTspQ6d7TKufaVAUK7Xxghi?filename=38z4530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38z4530.jpg&h=95165ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車撞向大廈外牆停下(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYCYdEHdVTTGemZkCyuGZMWzREJdzSxZrJJNrJNbUqBik?filename=f651591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff651591.jpg&h=a67cfb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傷者送院治理(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQqLFAkdbea1i9Tttz2bMr3voo4bMZUu2b4Zra4mwAiLz?filename=0c8v6Ub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0c8v6Ub.jpg&h=8605cf36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到場調查(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVEZYm6bYQMMdnAuLdjB2QFd9PJGZWGZuysE7x3VXcHXN?filename=ROEdW7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROEdW7e.jpg&h=c87844d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肇事私家車原本停在相中警車位置(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP8CexqD8s6rVfXhi62oeNhnVUZNEpYbXb2VxGrsRTjBw?filename=690PK85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F690PK85.jpg&h=d44f74b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在私家車車尾箱撿獲輪椅(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdzowam2QPfbMo4jv4yD6eVuWnrpnxy3j6KKYpBE2BPv5?filename=51Xf8s6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51Xf8s6.jpg&h=d39abd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車撞到燈柱(譚健文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/18/133625_da692fd0ea8960e28833f2bd48a54d81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2F133625_da692fd0ea8960e28833f2bd48a54d81.jpg&h=958c29b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車倒後撞到路牌(譚健文攝)<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7ea526ef698a44a987988e00c550eda2b69c3d29","tid":85102,"uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似自殺嘅喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又倒車又盛應該唔係"}]}